What is the weather in NYC?

how many skills do you have?
```

---

## Web UI Test

```sh
cd  apps/v8/app
uvicorn main:app --reload

docker compose -f apps/v8/docker-compose.yaml up -d --build
```

---

## Push to ECR

```sh
# login
aws ecr get-login-password --region ca-central-1 | docker login --username AWS --password-stdin 099139718958.dkr.ecr.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com

# create repo
aws ecr create-repository --repository-name ai-agent --region ca-central-1

# Push
docker build -t ai_agent_demo apps/v8
# tag
docker tag ai_agent_demo 099139718958.dkr.ecr.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/ai-agent
# push to docker
docker push 099139718958.dkr.ecr.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/ai-agent

# tag 
docker tag ai_agent_demo simonangelfong/ai-agent
docker push simonangelfong/ai-agent
```
